install (windows):
(1): https://nodejs.org/en
(2): npm install -g degit

if error : 
  - degit : File C:\Users\ikhsan.n\AppData\Roaming\npm\degit.ps1 cannot be loaded because running scripts is disabled on this system.

  - open Windows PowerShell as Administrator
  - run : Set-ExecutionPolicy -ExecutionPolicy RemoteSigned

  if success :
  run (2)

terminal at htdocs
(3): degit sveltejs/template myproject
(4): npm install
(5): npm run dev


